caption: Blue denim offers southern Cajun food and their menu changes every month or so. My all time favorites have been the crawfish fettuccine, shrimp n grits, and crawfish beignets. Other dishes that I've tried and have enjoyed are the boudin balls, duck confit, beignets & coffee, and NC trout. recommend
